tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditionally Exempt: 56th qualifier from Qualifying Tournament, Money List 61-100
tourBios.carHigh: Has played on the Hooters Tour and eGolf Tour while also competing in Georgia PGA section events. 2012: Advanced to the final stage of the PGA TOUR Qualifying Tournament for the first time and earned conditional status on the Web.com Tour after finishing T139...Played in the PGA Championship at the Ocean Course at Kiawah Island after qualifying through the PGA Professional National Championship...Made one start on the Web.com Tour, missing the cut at the Stadion Classic at UGA.
tourBios.personal: His father Bill Murchison Jr. played more than 65 times on the PGA TOUR and had 90 Web.com Tour appearances, including a victory in 1995 at the Tallahassee Open...Was home-schooled...Has his PGA Class A certification from the PGA Professional Golf Management program and serves as an assistant golf professional...Has seven sisters and two brothers...Favorite golf memory was riding in the golf-range picker at age 5...Is an Atlanta Braves, Atlanta Falcons and Atlanta Hawks fan...Never travels without headphones...Twitter account is @Bill_Murchison3.
